<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="lead text-center mb-5">Hüseyin Çağatay Çapar Law Office is committed to protecting your privacy.</p>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We collect information from you when you:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Contact us through our website</li>
                        <li>Schedule a consultation</li>
                        <li>Engage our legal services</li>
                        <li>Subscribe to our newsletter</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>The information we collect may include your name, email address, phone number, and information about your legal matter. We only collect information that is necessary to provide you with the legal services you request.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide legal services</li>
                        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
                        <li>Send periodic emails regarding legal updates or firm news</li>
                        <li>Process transactions and maintain records</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>All information is treated with strict confidentiality in accordance with our professional obligations as attorneys.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Attorney-Client Privilege and Confidentiality</h2>
                    <p>All communications between our law office and our clients are protected by attorney-client privilege. We maintain strict confidentiality of all client information as required by legal and professional ethics standards.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Data Security</h2>
                    <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. These measures include:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Secure data storage systems</li>
                        <li>Encrypted communications</li>
                        <li>Regular security assessments</li>
                        <li>Limited access to personal information</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
                    <p>Our website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience and collect information about how you use our site. You can set your browser to refuse cookies or alert you when cookies are being sent.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Third-Party Disclosure</h2>
                    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as required by law or to fulfill our professional obligations in representing you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
                        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
                        <li>Request deletion of your information (subject to legal requirements)</li>
                        <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page and updating the effective date below.</p>
                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 1, 2024</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us at:</p>
                    <p class="mb-0">Hüseyin Çağatay Çapar Law Office<br>
                    Mecidiyeköy Mah., Büyükdere Cad.<br>
                    Şişli, Istanbul 34394<br>
                    Turkey (Near Cevahir Shopping Mall)<br>
                    Email: privacy@capar-law.com<br>
                    Phone: +90 555 123 4567</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
